                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-09-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 11, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.
                            (Received September 12.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson announces that all telegrams viséed by the minister of marine
                        and written in plain language may be transmitted from this day.</p>
